udents are also required to complete a project on programming and applications."}, "outline": {"ch": "一、 了解基本程式設計原理\n二、 能實際運用於解決自身問題\n三、 能運用程式設計知能與應用完成團隊及個人作品", "en": "1. Understand the basic principles of programming\n2. Can be practically applied to solve their problems\n3. Be able to use programming knowledge and application to complete team and individual works"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1、陳會安。(2020)。Python 從初學到生活應用超實務：讓 Python 幫你處理日常生活與工作中繁瑣重複的工作。博碩文化。\n2、林志瑜。(2021)。初學Python的第一本書 : 從基本語法到模組應用（iT邦幫忙鐵人賽系列書）。博碩文化。", "en": "1. Chen Hoi An. (2020). Python from beginners to super practical life applications: let Python help you deal with the tedious and repetitive tasks in daily life and work. Ph.D. culture.\n2. Lin Zhiyu. (2021). The first book for beginners to Python: from basic syntax to module application (iT Bang Help Ironman series books). Ph.D. culture."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "80", "en": "80"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1.出席率：10％\n2.平時作業、課堂活動：40％\n3.提案、小組專題(錄制報告影片)：15％ + 35％", "en": "1. Attendance: 10％\n2. Daily homework and classroom activities: 40％\n3. Proposal, group topic (report video): 15％ + 35％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三12:00-13:00(請先預約)", "en": "Wednesday 12:00-13:00 ( by appointment)"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "安排自主學習活動", "en": "Independent learning activities"}, "domain": {"ch": "人文與文化研究領域", "en": "人文與文化研究領域"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "具備客家語言文化的基本能力", "rating": "(0)無", "assesments": ["無"]}, {"competencies": "具備社會科學的學科能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "具備人文關懷的精神", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["作業練習", "實作/實驗", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "具備掌握時勢脈動與創新發展的視野", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "The basic ability of Hakka language and culture", "rating": "(0)", "assesments": ["No a